    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度债券因借贷计划令市场失望而逆转涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-government-leaves-borrowing-largely-unchanged-bonds-lower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府未能满足交易员对印度政府大幅削减债务规模的预期，印度债券市场扭转了涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-government-leaves-borrowing-largely-unchanged-bonds-lower</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
